# helios.ai.toc — OpenClaw/Helios

## What This Is
OpenClaw/Helios is an advanced AI agent platform combining OpenClaw's core gateway infrastructure with Helios extensions for autonomous reasoning, memory management, and multi-modal interaction. It supports multi-agent orchestration, long-term memory with semantic search, browser automation, device control, and inter-agent messaging.

## Quick Start
```bash
# Install dependencies
pnpm install

# Set up environment
cp .env.example .env
# Edit .env with API keys

# Start gateway
openclaw gateway start

# In another terminal, start chat
openclaw chat
```

